oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Home belonging to Lindolph Orr
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the home belonging to Lindolph Orr. The people shown are David Orr; Lindolph Orr; Zellnar Orr; Iva Orr; Ann Jackson Barrett Orr; Bertha Burns; and Les Orr. There are three mules in the yard.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Mules; Houses; Families
